<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Autorizar Acceso — WhatsApp Masivo</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --green: #25D366;
            --green-glow: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.3);
            --green-soft: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.1);
            --bg: #0a0d12;
            --surface: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            --text: #e8edf5;
            --text-muted: #6b7a99;
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.07) 0%, transparent 70%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 90% 90%, rgba(37, 80, 180, 0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
        }

        .login-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
            box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        /* Subtle top glow line */
        .login-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(37,211,102,0.4), transparent);
        }

        /* App icon */
        .app-icon {
            width: 68px;
            height: 68px;
            background: var(--green-soft);
            border: 1px solid rgba(37,211,102,0.25);
            border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
            box-shadow: 0 0 24px var(--green-glow);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.65;
            margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
            max-width: 300px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .btn-google {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.65rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25D366 0%, #1db855 100%);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.95rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            width: 100%;
            transition: all 0.25s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--green-glow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-google::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-google:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--green-glow);
        }

        .btn-google:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

        .btn-google:active { transform: translateY(0); }

        /* Google G icon */
        .btn-google .g-icon {
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }

        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            color: rgba(107, 122, 153, 0.6);
        }

        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="login-card">
        <div class="app-icon">💬</div>
        <h1>Conectar Google Drive</h1>
        <p>Para gestionar mensajes e imágenes, la aplicación necesita acceso a tu cuenta de Google Drive.</p>

        <a href="<%= authUrl %>" class="btn-google">
            <span class="g-icon">G</span>
            Autorizar con Google
        </a>

        <p class="footer-note">Tus datos son privados y seguros.</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
